  "subject": "Add DMaaP simulator for CSIT testing",
  "commit_message": "Add DMaaP simulator for CSIT testing\n\nA rudimentary DMaaP simulator that simply holds requests and responds to all\nreaders with whatever message comes in on a topic.\n\nThe simulator is placed in policy PAP for now but should be\nsubmitted to DMaaP.\n\nThe simulator is now working but is still extremely rough.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-1643\nChange-Id: I76c996fc9237b0d76895dd7712b89dea3575bebd\nSigned-off-by: liamfallon <liam.fallon@est.tech>\n",
